Forts.: [ca. 29. Februar 1868]
I thank you for the news about yourself and Louise Maurus. Please give her
our love when you see her and inquire about her health.

Next sunday papa has to preache in Stamheim We read in our morning services
the old testament to day it was about Aron having made a Calf. it is to me
a real blessing to hear again about those different types of our Lord. papa
takes a good deal of troubel to explain us all he reads.

                              Adieu dear Son
